  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROMOTION!!!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/794570/extras/dcf127eadf366a3c3c2dffe6d2405e24.avif?t=1521772786\" width=90 height=90 /></span><br>Now you can get this game for only $0.11 or less on <br><br><br>XBall Champion is a casual sport game with unique game play.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>1. Very simple game play rules<br>2. Singleplayer & multiplayer modes<br>3. Steam achievement<br><br><strong>Controls</strong><br>1. Classical FPS control scheme (WSAD move & Mouse look)<br>2. Left mouse button for dash (only available when dash icon shown)<br><br><strong>Rules</strong><br>1. Hit the <i>exited</i> (highlighted) ball to get into <i>exited state</i><br>2. Score a goal in <i>exited</i> state<br>3. Team with higher score win the game",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROMOTION!!!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/794570/extras/dcf127eadf366a3c3c2dffe6d2405e24.avif?t=1521772786\" width=90 height=90 /></span><br>Now you can get this game for only $0.11 or less on <br><br><br>XBall Champion is a casual sport game with unique game play.<br><br><strong>Features</strong><br>1. Very simple game play rules<br>2. Singleplayer & multiplayer modes<br>3. Steam achievement<br><br><strong>Controls</strong><br>1. Classical FPS control scheme (WSAD move & Mouse look)<br>2. Left mouse button for dash (only available when dash icon shown)<br><br><strong>Rules</strong><br>1. Hit the <i>exited</i> (highlighted) ball to get into <i>exited state</i><br>2. Score a goal in <i>exited</i> state<br>3. Team with higher score win the game",
